<p>We have a great solution! Come and check out our recommendations. Accommodating from 10 - 60 people, these luxury groups are the way to go. Extra discounts for multiple bookings may apply!</p>

<h3>Base Camp Group Lodging</h3>

<p>BASE CAMP on JANE CREEK: Together these three exquisite 4 bedroom ski-in/ski-out properties can easily accommodate a group of 23. Pull out sleeper sofas or air beds provide sleeping space for 6 additional people. Set on the edge of the Arapaho National Forest, alongside Jane Creek and mid-way on the ski corridor between Mary Jane and Winter Park, these properties offer the very best in a ski-in/ski-out location. Located just a few yards from each other, you can combine the privacy of individual accommodations and the fun of a group get-together.</p>

