<h3>Lakota Group Lodging</h3>

<p>LAKOTA & ANTLERS @ LAKOTA: Together these three gorgeous ski base area properties can easily accommodate a group of 30. Sleeper sofas and/or air beds in the properties would allow sleeping space for an additional 4 people. Set in a in the prestigious Lakota community just opposite the Winter Park ski resort, these properties offer amazing views, private hot tubs, upscale furnishings and a Colorado mountain lodge style ambience. Located just a short walk from each other, you can combine the privacy of individual accommodations and the great fun of a group get-together.</p>

<p><strong>Access Winter Park Lakota properties:</strong><br />
<a href="/property/antlers-401-at-lakota">Antlers #401 at Lakota</a> (sleeps 10)<br />
