<h3>Slopeside Village Group Lodging</h3>

<p>SLOPESIDE VILLAGE: Together these five  base area properties can easily accommodate a group of 39. Pull out sleeper sofas or air beds provide sleeping space for 4 additional people. Set on the northern edge of Winter Park Resort ski area, Slopeside Village offers the convenience of being in the base area without the noise, traffic and congestion of the central resort. It is even possible to ski-in!. The complimentary resort shuttle stops at the entrance to Slopeside Village and whisks you to the lifts in less than 2 minutes.  It's perhaps a 7 minute walk to the lifts. These properties offer an unbeatable base area location. Located just a snowball's throw from each other, you can combine the privacy of individual accommodations with the fun of a group get-together</p>

