<h3>Trademark Group Lodging</h3>

<p>TRADEMARK: Together these three gorgeous ski base area properties can easily accommodate a group of 24. Add in neighboring Winter Park Place properties  and we have beds for 30. Sleeper sofas in the properties would allow sleeping space for an additional 4 people. Set in a private gated enclave in the ski base area,within walking distance of the lifts and set on the Fraser River at the Fraser River Trailhead, these properties have it all!  Trademark offers a large in-ground common area hot tub. Trademark 3-4 and Trademark 3-2 also have private hot tubs on the deck overlooking the ski area. Stunning views, luxurious comfort, convenience are just a few of the reasons to choose to stay at Trademark. Located just a few yards from each other, you can combine the privacy of individual accommodations and the great fun of a group get-together. Plan your next family reunion here!</p>

